stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Pending: Create Task

    state Pending {
        [*] --> AwaitingStart: Wait for startTime
        AwaitingStart --> ReadyToStart: startTime reached
    }

    Pending --> InProgress: User starts task
    Pending --> Completed: Auto-complete (0 subtasks)

    state InProgress {
        [*] --> ActiveWork
        ActiveWork --> WaitingFeedback: Need review
        WaitingFeedback --> ActiveWork: Feedback received
    }

    InProgress --> Completed: All subtasks done
    InProgress --> Pending: User pauses task

    state Completed {
        [*] --> Done
        Done --> Archived: After 30 days
    }

    Completed --> InProgress: Reopen task

    state SubTask {
        [*] --> Pending: Create subtask
        Pending --> Completed: Toggle complete
        Completed --> Pending: Toggle incomplete
        Pending --> [*]: Delete subtask
        Completed --> [*]: Delete subtask
    }

    note right of Pending
        Task stays in Pending
        until startTime or
        user manually starts
    end note

    note right of InProgress
        Task is active
        Subtasks can be
        added/updated
    end note

    note right of Completed
        Task is done
        Read-only mode
        Auto-archived after TTL
    end note

    note left of SubTask
        Subtasks are in
        separate collection
        Virtual populate
    end note
